, engineering-first."},{year:"2020",title:"First EHR Integration — PointClickCare",desc:"Shipped our first bi-directional EHR integration with PointClickCare, delivering real-time vital sign sync to senior living facilities across the US. Deep integration, zero complexity."},{year:"2021",title:"Five Medicare Programs, One Platform",desc:"Expanded from RPM to deliver CCM, PCM, BHI, and RTM on a single unified platform — automated billing, compliant time tracking, and clinical documentation across all five Medicare programs."},{year:"2022",title:"Nationwide — 50-State Coverage",desc:"Deployed across all 50 states with enterprise-grade HIPAA infrastructure. Supporting providers at every scale — from solo practitioners to multi-facility health systems with thousands of patients."},{year:"2023",title:"25+ FDA-Cleared Devices Integrated",desc:"Built the industry's most device-agnostic platform: 25+ FDA-cleared monitors from Tenovi, Omron, Dexcom, BodyTrace, Xandar Kardian, Withings, and more. Any device, any patient, no vendor lock-in."},{year:"2024",title:"1B+ Data Transactions Processed",desc:"Surpassed one billion data transactions — vital signs, clinical alerts, care documentation, and billing events flowing in real time between devices, clinical staff, EHR systems, and Medicare programs."},{year:"2025",title:"Contactless & Next-Gen Device Integration",desc:"Pioneering the next frontier of remote monitoring: contactless radar-based vital sign detection (Xandar Kardian, Neteera), continuous glucose monitoring (Dexcom G7), and AI-driven predictive alerting — redefining what's possible in remote care."}],w=[{icon:s.Target,title:"Mission-Driven",desc:"We exist to make remote care management accessible, efficient, and scalable for healthcare teams of every size.",gradient:"from-violet-500/20 to-blue-500/20",iconColor:"text-violet-500",iconBg:"bg-violet-500/10"},{icon:i.Cpu,title:"Engineering-First",desc:"We automate the mundane so clinical staff can focus on what matters most — their patients. Every feature reduces clicks, not adds them.",gradient:"from-blue-500/20 to-cyan-500/20",iconColor:"text-[#256eff]",iconBg:"bg-[#256eff]/10"},{icon:r.Users,title:"User-First Design",desc:"Every workflow, every screen, every interaction is designed around the people who use our platform every day — nurses, care coordinators, and billers.",gradient:"from-cyan-500/20 to-emerald-500/20",iconColor:"text-cyan-600",iconBg:"bg-cyan-500/10"}],j=[{icon:m.Shield,title:"HIPAA Compliant",desc:"Every layer of the platform is engineered for HIPAA compliance from the ground up."},{icon:h.Lock,title:"End-to-End Encryption",desc:"Data encrypted in transit and at rest. TLS 1.3, AES-256, role-based access controls."},{icon:f.FileCheck,title:"BAA Included",desc:"Business Associate Agreements with every infrastructure partner and customer."},{icon:p.Server,title:"SOC 2 Certified",desc:"Continuous monitoring, regular penetration testing, and audit-ready documentation."}],_=[{quote:"When we brought the Xandar Kardian integration to market with CCN Health, their team moved faster than any partner we've worked with. From technical integration to live patient monitoring in weeks — they made a complex three-way partnership feel effortless.",name:"Andrew Wheeler",role:"VP, GTM Strategy & Operations",org:"Tenovi",logo:"/assets/partners/manufacturer/tenovi.svg"},{quote:"Working with CCN was so easy. Their CEO took the time to meet with our providers and walk them through how to use their clinical dashboard. We absolutely made the right decision to go with CCN.",name:"Robin Shelton",role:"Quality Assurance",org:"Rural Health Services",logo:v.testimonials.ruralHealth},{quote:"Partnering with CCN Health has been a game-changer — they're everything we look for in an RPM vendor: highly organized, reliable, and incredibly fast at scaling.",name:"Steve Wheeler",role:"VP of Partnerships",org:"Tenovi",logo:"/assets/partners/manufacturer/tenovi.svg"},{quote:"This company is amazing! So easy to work with and very responsive to all requests. It's great to have all our patient vitals flowing directly into their charts.",name:"Stephanie Bryant-Lipp",role:"Senior Quality Manager",org:"Village Medical",logo:v.testimonials.villageMedical},{quote:"Heart failure admissions have decreased noticeably. Over the last three years, we've seen fewer heart attacks and hospitalizations, significantly due to our monitoring efforts with CCN Health.",name:"Dr. Dawn Atwal, MD",role:"Cardiologist",org:"Laguna Cardiology",logo:""},{quote:"CCN Health's Caregiver App transformed our care delivery. It empowered our nursing teams to monitor numerous patients using minimal equipment, significantly reducing overhead costs.",name:"Facility Manager",role:"Operations",org:"Access Healthcare Associates",logo:""},{quote:"CCN Health's device-agnostic approach is exactly what the RPM market needs. They integrate any FDA-cleared device we ship — cellular, Bluetooth, or contactless — without forcing providers into a single vendor ecosystem.",name:"Andrew Wheeler",role:"VP, GTM Strategy & Operations",org:"Tenovi",logo:"/assets/partners/manufacturer/tenovi.svg"},{quote:"Most RPM vendors take months to onboard a new device line. CCN Health had our latest cellular monitors integrated and live with patients in under two weeks. That speed is unheard of in this space.",name:"Steve Wheeler",role:"VP of Partnerships",org:"Tenovi",logo:"/assets/partners/manufacturer/tenovi.svg"},{quote:"CCN Health transformed how we deliver care. The integration with PointClickCare was seamless, and the clinical support team handles everything. Our staff can focus on residents instead of technology.",name:"Sarah Mitchell",role:"Director of Clinical Services",org:"Sunrise Senior Living",logo:""}];function N(){let[e,s]=(0,t.useState)(0);return(0,a.jsxs)(a.Fragment,{children:[(0,a.jsxs)("section",{className:"relative bg-hero-hub overflow-hidden texture-noise-heavy texture-scanlines",children:[(0,a.jsx)("div",{cla